name: 30-minute Skype Guitar Lesson
description:
A 30-minute guitar lesson over Skype.
NOTE: You MUST have a Skype account and a functioning webcam in order to conduct the lesson. Once purchased, you will receive a confirmation e-mail that provides you with a calendar of availability. Please send an e-mail back with the time and date of your choice. If you would like to be contacted at an e-mail other than the one provided through Paypal, please send this info to seanguitarlessons@gmail.com **Refunds for cancellations will not be given unless informed 24 hours prior to the scheduled lesson**
